Update: Cambiguous is a project that I (Mike) started with music video production in mind. I spent 3 years making tons of videos with some truly remarkable musicians, and it was some of the most fun i've ever had. In July of 2018 I started a new journey with @oneislandmedia, a production company specializing in the communication of social and environmental research through video. While I'm no longer actively shooting music videos, i'm not completely closing the door on Cambiguous. It will still exist for the occasional music video and personal project that I feel like posting, so stick around if you're interested in that. Here's one such video, a compilation of moments that didn't make any commercial projects over the course of 2019 so far.
